    Internet provider for United States

    Source: R/internet-provider-en_US.R
    InternetProvider_en_US.Rd

    methods for internet related data, like email addresses, usernames, and websites.

    Method clone()

    The objects of this class are cloneable with this method.

    Usage

    InternetProvider_en_US$clone(deep = FALSE)

    Arguments

    deep

    Whether to make a deep clone.

    Examples

    x <- InternetProvider_en_US$new()
x$email()
#> [1] "jbeer@hotmail.com"
x$free_email()
#> [1] "jovanny.kunde@yahoo.com"
x$mac_address()
#> [1] "dd:de:55:cf:9e:73:29"
x$company_email()
#> [1] "thomas.reynolds@donnelly.com"
